            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " as some have accused me of simply hating everything the man does, which I’ve pointed out isn’t true. Look, despite what black-and-white thinkers try to push, I and anyone else can like ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
